            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 8
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "生徒会室での情事から、１時間ほどして——\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 9
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 19
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "俺たちは、夜の通学路を並んで歩いていた。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 20
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 23
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "火照った体をねっとりとした夜風に撫でられて、服の下に\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 24
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "汗がにじむ。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 25
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 28
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "お祭りの前日にはぴったりの、夏らしい夜だった。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 29
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "いずみ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "IS011132"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 35
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「ふふっ」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 36
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 39
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "腕に抱きついてきたいずみ姉さんが、嬉しそうな笑い声を\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 40
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "たてる。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 41
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 44
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「どうしたの？」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 45
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "いずみ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "IS011133"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 51
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「私のお洋服から、かずちゃんの匂いがするの」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 52
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 55
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「っ……！　そ、それは……その、ごめん……」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 56
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "いずみ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "IS011134"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 61
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「どうして謝るの？　これからずっと、このお洋服\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 62
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　洗いたくないくらい嬉しいのに」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 63
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 66
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「それはさすがに、ちゃんと洗ってくれよ」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 67
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "いずみ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "IS011135"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 72
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「ふふっ、かずちゃんのケチ」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 73
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 76
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "そう言う表情も楽しげで、こっちまで嬉しくなってしまう。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 77
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "いずみ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "IS011136"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 83
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「でも、そうね……みんなにはまだ、知られない方が\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 84
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　いいでしょうね」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 85
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 88
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "いずみ姉さんは寂しげに微笑すると、俺の返答を待たずに\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 89
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "言葉をつないだ。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 90
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "いずみ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "IS011137"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 95
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「お母さんが機嫌を直してくれない限り、かずちゃんは\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 96
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　姉妹の中の誰かを選ばないといけない立場だものね」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 97
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "いずみ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "IS011138"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 103
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「いまは波風を立てるようなことをするべきではないわ」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 104
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 107
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「………………」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 108
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 113
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "いずみ姉さんの言うことにも一理あった。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 114
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 117
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "明日の夏祭りで仲直りをしてもらえることを信じては\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 118
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "いても、俺が姉妹の中の誰か一人と恋人同士になったと\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 119
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "あれば、不安をあおるようなことになりかねない。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 120
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "いずみ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "IS011139"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 126
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「ふふっ、それに、秘めやかな関係って、なんだか\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 127
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　いやらしくて素敵だものね」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 128
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 131
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「いずみ姉さん……」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 132
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "いずみ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "IS011140"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 137
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「もう、そんなにげっそりしたお顔をしないでかずちゃん」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 138
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "いずみ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "IS011141"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 143
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「物心がついたころからずっと想っていた、私の夢が\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 144
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　叶ったのよ、浮かれてしまっても仕方がないわ」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 145
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 148
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「……そんなに昔から？」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 149
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 152
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "むずがゆいくらいの嬉しさを感じて、俺はいずみ姉さんに\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 153
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "問いかけた。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 154
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "いずみ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "IS011142"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 160
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「ええ、そうよ……かずちゃんが、家出した私を初めて\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 161
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　迎えに来てくれた日から、ずっと、ずーっと\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 162
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　想っていたの」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 163
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "いずみ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "IS011143"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 168
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「だからいまこの瞬間も、現実だって信じられないくらい\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 169
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　幸せなのよ……？」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 170
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 173
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "母性すら感じるほどの優しいまなざしを向けられる。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 174
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "いずみ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "IS011144"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 179
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「ねえ、かずちゃん……」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 180
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 183
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「うん？」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 184
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "いずみ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "IS011145"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 190
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「両想いになるって、とってもすてきな気分ね」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 191
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 194
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「ああ……」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 195
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "いずみ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "IS011146"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 200
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「お父さんとお母さんも、こういう気持ちでいたことが\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 201
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　あったのでしょうね」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 202
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 205
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「そうだろうね」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 206
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 209
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "そうじゃなければ、結婚にまで踏み切ったりしないだろう。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 210
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "いずみ"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "IS011147"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 215
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「お父さんとお母さんは、明日のお祭りでこの気持ちを\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 216
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　思い出してくれるかしら？」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 217
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 220
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「大丈夫だよ、商店会の人たちだって学校のみんなだって\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 221
        },
